        <span class="property-type"><a href="#asymmetricencryptedsecret">Dict[Asymmetric<wbr>Encrypted<wbr>Secret]</a></span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The encryption key used to encrypt the data. This is a user secret.{{% /md %}}</dd>

</dl>
